data.description: Wonderful move in ready 3 bed, 2 1/2 bath in Waterford Green.  Walk in your new front door to enter your new home and relax. The kitchen offers an eat in dining area with space to cook and entertain. Off the kitchen is your laundry closet with storage.  Sit and enjoy yourself in a cozy family room with views of the garden. Half bath in the living room for easy access. Upstairs  you will find 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. This unit is one of few that has its own primary bathroom, a great feature to have! Bring your own custom touches to this home and make it one that you love. This is an end unit with side access to your back yard. Home is located close to Rt 30, Rt 73 and AC expressway and Atco transit station for an easy commute to Philadelphia and the Jersey Shore points. There are no HOA fees. This home is located in the Hammonton School District.
